# Mac build JDK (already installed)

Temurin JDK 21 is **already installed** at:

`.build-jdk/jdk-21.0.11+10/Contents/Home`

`gradle.properties` sets `org.gradle.java.home` to that path for `jpackage` / `copyCurrentBuilds`.

**Never download or install Temurin again** unless the user explicitly says it is missing or broken.

Before Mac/desktop builds, verify only:

```bash
test -x .build-jdk/jdk-21.0.11+10/Contents/Home/bin/jpackage
```

If missing, tell the user — do not curl/download automatically.
